# Token Efficiency

## Tool surface

- Default = 3 tools. New tools need `--full-tools` or strong justification in PR.
- Descriptions ≤ 1 short sentence.
- Prefer enums / optional params over long prose.

## Responses

- Columnar JSON only: `{"cols":[...],"rows":[[...]],"meta":{...}}`
- Cap rows (`max_rows`) and bytes (`max_bytes`); set `meta.truncated=true`
- EXPLAIN: distilled summary, not raw plan tree dump
- Errors: short actionable strings (mention which flag unlocks)

## Anti-patterns

- Schema dump tools in default mode
- Pretty markdown tables as default
- Returning passwords / connection URLs in tool output
